title: File:Prédio do Baleizão, Luanda - 2019-06-28.jpg
author: Edward Middleton
description:
Classified, historical building "Prédio do Baleizão", in Luanda, built in the 17th-century and one of the oldest of the city, 5 months after being evacuated and locked down by authorities, due to imminent ruin, in january 2019. Front view (facade), from Largo da Amizade Angola-Cuba.
(original title: Something old with something new, original description: a old building in Luanda with cars parked in front in Angola)
